  "detailed_description": "<strong>Kinetic Storm</strong> is a top-down arena shooter where you destroy waves of enemies and select upgrades at the end of the wave. It is a roguelike, so enemies and upgrades are randomly generated, and every play-through is radically different as you discover synergies between your weapon, skill, movement, and defence choices. Running on a custom Vulkan game engine, it is both visually stunning and highly performant with responsive low-latency controls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Powerful weapons</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/56584f995fdcccfab5a5f6df0dcfbf1b.poster.avif?t=1745263622\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/56584f995fdcccfab5a5f6df0dcfbf1b.webm?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/56584f995fdcccfab5a5f6df0dcfbf1b.mp4?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Before each run select your primary and secondary weapon. Focus on upgrading one, or carefully choose useful upgrades for each.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/58311c6eeeca599d97a12acff9c4a3ec.poster.avif?t=1745263622\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/58311c6eeeca599d97a12acff9c4a3ec.webm?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/58311c6eeeca599d97a12acff9c4a3ec.mp4?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Useful skills</h2><br>Manage your energy levels to make best use of your skills. A dash at just the right time can save your ship, or destroy masses of enemies ... if you have the right upgrades.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/56c8babbd4ae2934884566b5df02de1b.poster.avif?t=1745263622\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/56c8babbd4ae2934884566b5df02de1b.webm?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/56c8babbd4ae2934884566b5df02de1b.mp4?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique enemies</h2><br>Enemies are carefully designed to each have distinct abilities and defences. Some are deadly up close, others from far away, or only from some angles. Which will you destroy first?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/b704d4b1da9e1782b3ab678ec7098937.poster.avif?t=1745263622\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/b704d4b1da9e1782b3ab678ec7098937.webm?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/b704d4b1da9e1782b3ab678ec7098937.mp4?t=1745263622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deadly bosses</h2><br>Challenge massive and terrifying boss enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless upgrades</h2><br>Your reward for survival is ever increasing power and destructive ability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2154430/extras/07ecc77d10b6a49188bab2905afaaea8.avif?t=1745263622\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
